      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/t-rowe-manager-who-predicted-yen-shock-sees-another-one-coming</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿里夫·侯赛因表示，他很早就对去年日本利率上升发出了警告，他将此描述为“金融界的圣安德烈亚斯故障”。]]></description>
